  <div class="page-header">
    <h2>How To Mine</h2>
  </div>
  <p>In order to mine on this pool you need to have a stratum miner installation pointed to <code>{{config.StratumHost}}:{{config.StratumPort}}</code>
  </p>
   <p>
    <strong>Usage example:</strong>
    <code>WshDcrMiner64.exe -epool stratum+tcp://{{config.StratumHost}}:{{config.StratumPort}} -ewal YOUR_WSH_ADDRESS -epsw x -eworker RIG_ID</code>.<br/>
  </p>
  <dl class="dl-horizontal">
    <dt>YOUR_WSH_ADDRESS</dt>
    <dd>This is your address for payouts, generate one with gwsh, parity or 
      <a href="https://www.myetherwallet.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">MyEtherWallet</a>.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>0xc285f9dc21232fe887830234631adb9544e40d31</code>.
    </dd>
    <dt>RIG_ID</dt>
    <dd>
      ID of your farm to distinguish it from your other rig. If you have just one rig, feel free to omit this param.
      This param must be short alphanumeric string with optional dashes and underscores.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>rig-1</code>
    </dd>
  </dl>

  <p>It is also possible to set up a connection with Telegram bot:</p>
